---
title: Carb Smart Manila Style Turkey Stew with Jammy Eggs and Crispy Shallots
description: This recipe pulls heavily from Filipinx dinner time staple known as "Giniling,"  you will find both familiar and homey flavors in this stew. Traditionally served with steamed rice, this carb smart version opts instead to skip the starch in favour of doubling up on protein with the addition of jammy boiled eggs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-dinde-a-la-manillaise-5d5b85e2.jpg
